by jeremy-derusse at 2014-12-11T10:03:18Z

Can you, please, add the remarks from @stof (https://github.com/sensiolabs/melody/pull/24)

here is my proposal

```
<?php
<<<CONFIG
packages:
    - "silex/silex: *"
php-options:
    - "-S"
    - "localhost:8000"
CONFIG;

$app = new Silex\Application();
$app->get('/hello/{name}', function ($name) use ($app) {
    return 'Hello '.$app->escape($name);
});
$app->run();

Beware of YAML syntax:
* `- silex/silex: *` without quote is an invalid YAML
* `- silex/silex: ~1.2` without quote is a YAML object and refused by melody
* `- -S` without quote is an array of arrays
```

